<cu_txt_unit_wysiwyg>
<cs_txt_unit_wysiwyg>Given a named item under REFERENCES, say with the the name ‘ITM:Euler’, what should the cross reference ‘[ITM:Euler]’ look like? Assuming it is the first item on the list, one could either go for</cs_txt_unit_wysiwyg>
</cu_txt_unit_wysiwyg>
